- Why don't watermelons tell jokes? Because they always get the punchline wrong.
- I used to think that watermelons were just stupid fruits, but then I found out that they're actually really smart. They're 92% water and the rest is flavor.

If you want more let me know!

3. Why did the watermelon go to the doctor? Because it was feeling cantaloupy! And why did the watermelon want to join a band? Because it was already a big drum!
4. Here are some humorous quotes about water melons : 
- "I was going to do a laffy taffy joke. But something totally random happened when I was trying to brown the chocolate. It's probably a good thing though, as I heard there's about to be a massive wave of laffy taffy jokes on the sub." - Bren4892
- "American President: Our cause is just!
King: No it isn't. We have more legitimacy than you.
American President: We have really big weapons.
King: Big weapons don't give you rights.
American President: Watermelons do though." - B Progressive
